{"tid":1489932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter戰線嘅同我入來！！少少意見！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T03:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:02:59.000Z","uid":212944,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4d3554454cf0a382f2185401bc957ea56b78c1","tid":1489932,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:44:30.000Z","msg":"有幾點想提大家:<br />\n<br />\n1. 我地唔係網軍，係「傳道人」<br />\n唔該唔好淨係落hashtag，copy人地口號，加少少自己嘅comment同感受。人地唔係想睇洗版，而係有血有肉嘅香港人有咩睇法。<br />\n<br />\n2. 盡量打英文，唔好打香港人先睇得明嘅野。唔使怕英文差grammar 錯，睇得明就得。其實外國人會更加appreciate non-native speaker努力同佢地explain香港發生緊咩事<br />\n<br />\n3. retweet都加返少少comment同hashtag<br />\n4. 可以mon住各大外媒(路透社,CNN,BBC etc)，每逢有Post關於HK 同中國都可以入去comment下，用傾計嘅心態同鬼佬溝通，記得要有禮貌。擔心自己英文差可以講聲sorry for the poor english. (但通常佢地都唔會介意)<br />\n<br />\n5. 對住中國愛國小粉紅，唔使動氣。有D叻D嘅會用英文同你講野，你就可以逐點擊破/唔理佢。用中文講野嘅更加可以用返英文大鳩佢。<br />\n<br />\n6. 個人覺得可以將重點放喺：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>feminism 同 hate speech</strong></span><br />\n性侵犯同埋「曱甴」言論其實係general 左翼極度討厭嘅嘢。必須大力推<br />\n出feminism related嘅post可以加 #boycottmulan ， 同加句 &ldquo;Is that what Liu Yi-Fei supports?&rdquo; 效果更佳<br />\n<br />\n7. 文宣組請考慮出多啲英文memes <br />\n<br />\n暫時分享係咁多，大家加油"},{"pid":"a399356d8a871d8d78b7c4d1f98b32b1f80fb0e9","tid":1489932,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"同意 推推推"},{"pid":"1775a7f277b55643cfd59b0c62cc191fa558c9b2","tid":1489932,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"ea6f5558e24535106ec5a3e93f552f695d12eb79","tid":1489932,"uid":154277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議文宣圖加英文"},{"pid":"8a45c482766dc38d047e5bea9cbf6f32ce92ad5f","tid":1489932,"uid":108337,"lik